---
import { Button } from 'astro-pure/user'
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import config from '@/site-config'

const meta = {
  title: 'Disclaimer',
  description: 'Last updated: 2026-02-28'
}

const contact = (config as any).contact || {
  email: 'qiatao0305@163.com',
  website: 'https://your-website.com',
  region: 'China'
}
---

<PageLayout {meta}>
  <Button title='Back' href='/terms' variant='back' />
  <main class='mt-6 lg:mt-10'>
    <div id='content-header' class='animate'>
      <h1 class='mb-6 text-3xl font-medium'>Disclaimer / 免责声明</h1>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>Last Updated: February 28, 2026 / 最后更新：2026年2月28日</p>
    </div>

    <div id='content' class='animate mt-8 prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none'>
      <h2>General Information / 一般信息</h2>
      <p>The information on this website is provided on an "as is" basis. To the fullest extent permitted by law, this website:</p>
      <p>本网站上的信息按"现状"提供。在法律允许的最大范围内，本网站：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Excludes all representations, warranties, conditions, and terms relating to this website and the use of this website (including, without limitation, any warranties implied by law) / 排除与本网站和使用本网站有关的所有声明、保证、条件和条款（包括但不限于法律暗示的任何保证）</li>
        <li>Excludes all liability for damages arising out of or in connection with your use of this website / 排除因使用本网站或与使用本网站相关而产生的所有损害责任</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>No Warranty / 无保证</h2>
      <p>We make no representations or warranties of any kind, express or implied, about:</p>
      <p>我们不提供任何形式的明示或暗示的声明或保证，关于：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The completeness, accuracy, reliability, suitability, or availability of the website or the information, products, services, or related graphics contained on the website / 网站的完整性、准确性、可靠性、适用性或可用性，或网站上包含的信息、产品、服务或相关图形</li>
        <li>The results that may be obtained from the use of this website / 使用本网站可能获得的结果</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability / 责任限制</h2>
      <p>To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, in no event shall we be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including without limitation, loss of profits, data, use, goodwill, or other intangible losses, resulting from:</p>
      <p>在法律允许的最大范围内，在任何情况下，我们均不对任何直接、间接、偶然、特殊、后果性或惩罚性损害承担责任，包括但不限于利润、数据、使用、商誉或其他无形损失，这些损失由以下原因造成：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your use or inability to use the website / 您使用或无法使用网站</li>
        <li>Any unauthorized access to or use of our servers and/or any personal information stored therein / 任何未经授权访问或使用我们的服务器和/或其中存储的任何个人信息</li>
        <li>Any interruption or cessation of transmission to or from our website / 传输到或从我们网站的任何中断或停止</li>
        <li>Any bugs, viruses, trojan horses, or the like, which may be transmitted to or through our website / 可能传输到或通过我们网站的任何错误、病毒、特洛伊木马或类似内容</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>External Links / 外部链接</h2>
      <p>This website may contain links to external websites that are not provided or maintained by us. We do not guarantee the accuracy, relevance, timeliness, or completeness of any information on these external websites.</p>
      <p>本网站可能包含指向非我们提供或维护的外部网站的链接。我们不保证这些外部网站上任何信息的准确性、相关性、及时性或完整性。</p>
      <p>The inclusion of any link does not imply endorsement by us of the site. Use of any such linked website is at the user's own risk.</p>
      <p>包含任何链接并不意味着我们认可该网站。使用任何此类链接网站的风险由用户自行承担。</p>

      <h2>Professional Advice / 专业建议</h2>
      <p>The content on this website is for general information purposes only and does not constitute professional advice. You should not rely on the information on this website as an alternative to professional advice.</p>
      <p>本网站上的内容仅供一般信息目的，不构成专业建议。您不应依赖本网站上的信息作为专业建议的替代。</p>
      <p>If you have any specific questions about any matter, you should consult an appropriate professional.</p>
      <p>如果您对任何事项有任何具体问题，您应该咨询适当的专业人士。</p>

      <h2>Technical Issues / 技术问题</h2>
      <p>We do not warrant that:</p>
      <p>我们不保证：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>This website will be available at all times or be uninterrupted / 本网站将始终可用或不会中断</li>
        <li>The information on this website is complete, true, accurate, or non-misleading / 本网站上的信息完整、真实、准确或不误导</li>
        <li>This website is free from defects, errors, bugs, or viruses / 本网站没有缺陷、错误、错误或病毒</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Changes to Content / 内容变更</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to make additions, deletions, or modifications to the contents of this website at any time without prior notice.</p>
      <p>我们保留随时对本网站内容进行添加、删除或修改的权利，恕不另行通知。</p>

      <h2>User Responsibility / 用户责任</h2>
      <p>Your use of this website and any dispute arising out of such use of the website is subject to the laws of {contact.region}.</p>
      <p>您使用本网站以及因使用本网站而产生的任何争议均受{contact.region}法律管辖。</p>
      <p>You are responsible for ensuring that your use of this website complies with all applicable laws and regulations.</p>
      <p>您有责任确保您使用本网站符合所有适用的法律法规。</p>

      <h2>Contact Information / 联系信息</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this Disclaimer, please contact us:</p>
      <p>如果您对本免责声明有任何疑问，请联系我们：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href={`mailto:${contact.email}`}>{contact.email}</a> / 电子邮件：<a href={`mailto:${contact.email}`}>{contact.email}</a></li>
        <li>Website: <a href={contact.website} target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>{contact.website}</a> / 网站：<a href={contact.website} target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>{contact.website}</a></li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <p><em>This Disclaimer was last updated on February 28, 2026. / 本免责声明最后更新于2026年2月28日。</em></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</PageLayout>
